      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "和埃米爾閒聊了起來。",
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "只有細心留意，才能發掘生活中的美。而珍惜這些細小的美好，我覺得，就是浪漫的本質哦~",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "options": [
        {
          "content": "好奇",
          "flag": 1
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "生活中的美好東西有許多呢，即使每天都是一樣的環境，其中也會有細微的變化。",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "今天的鳥兒叫聲是不是和昨天不一樣呢？這裡有一朵沒有見過的花呢~在不同的地方跳舞的感覺也完全不同……",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "埃米爾閉上雙眼，雙手抱在胸前，像是在擁抱著什麼美好的東西一樣。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "和人交流也是一樣的，世上不存在兩個性格完全一樣的人，即使看起來相似，也一定存在著某些差異。",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "去發現每個人身上的不同，我覺得是十分重要的~",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "而且指揮官你不覺得，如果發現一個人身上有非常美好的品質，會是一件十分開心的事嗎？",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "options": [
        {
          "content": "點頭",
          "flag": 1
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "所以呢，雖然也會有難過和悲傷的時候，不過只要想到世界上還有那麼多值得我去體驗和發現的東西，就覺得一定要堅持下去。",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "離別也好，戰爭也好，哪怕有多麼痛苦，只要我的這份熱情沒有消退，我就永遠不會屈服。",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "……",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "埃米爾回過神來，露出有點不好意思的表情",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "啊哈哈，好像說了一些非常自大的話，有點不好意思呢…指揮官你聽過就算了哦？",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "不過她馬上像是想到了什麼一樣湊了過來。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "對了，指揮官！我們來約會吧~",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "你看，既然聊到了浪漫，比起說些大道理，來實踐不是更好的方法嗎？",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
